Sunbird‚Äôs Recommendation
Instead of Local Power Panels, Sunbird recommends using Remote Power Panels under the RPPs.
With Remote Power Panels:
Panels can have different / unique names
Mirroring is still supported
There is no functional change in behavior
The only difference is in the one-line diagram, where Remote Panels will appear slightly below / outside the RPP (Floor PDU) boundary. Sunbird confirmed this is a visual placement difference only.
